; Regression test for issue #847: dated balance assertions should respect
; date ordering, not file ordering.  A balance assertion dated 2010-01-02
; appearing after a transaction dated 2010-01-03 should only consider
; postings through 2010-01-02.

2010-01-01 * Starting Balance
    Assets:Bank:Checking            1000.00 EUR
    Equity:Opening-Balances

2010-01-02 * Shopping
    Expenses:Shopping                 10 EUR
    Assets:Bank:Checking

2010-01-03 * Some more shopping
    Expenses:Shopping                  5 EUR
    Assets:Bank:Checking

; Balance assertion dated before the last transaction in the file.
; The balance of Assets:Bank:Checking as of 2010-01-02 is 990.00 EUR
; (1000 - 10), regardless of the 2010-01-03 transaction.
2010-01-02 * Balance Check
    Assets:Bank:Checking            0 EUR = 990.00 EUR

test balance
          985.00 EUR  Assets:Bank:Checking
        -1000.00 EUR  Equity:Opening-Balances
           15.00 EUR  Expenses:Shopping
--------------------
                   0
end test
